  "name": "Morrison COU2 — VAD hemolysis credibility assessment (Minimal profile)",
  "description": "V&V 40 credibility assessment for CFD hemolysis prediction of the FDA generic centrifugal blood pump under ventricular assist device (VAD) conditions. This package evaluates whether the computational model can predict absolute hemolysis levels for a Class III VAD device at Model Risk Level 5. The intended use scope — regulatory submission support for a Class III implantable VAD operating at 5 L/min, 3500 RPM, with blood-contacting surfaces — is described in the bound requirement and claim documents. Monte Carlo uncertainty quantification was performed; all 13 credibility factors were assessed against MRL-5 thresholds. Decision: Accepted with conditions documented in the decision record.",
  "bindsRequirement": "https://uofa.net/synth/req/vad-hemolysis-mrl5-requirement",
  "bindsClaim": "https://uofa.net/synth/claim/vad-cfd-hemolysis-prediction-claim",
  "bindsModel": "https://uofa.net/synth/model/fda-centrifugal-pump-cfd-hemolysis-v2",
